Chapter 5
Port forwarding (Router Users, Using Linksys)
You don’t use linksys? Find your router at
http://www.portforward.com/english/routers/port_forwarding/routerindex.htm
and follow the tutorial.

Open your cmd by going to Start > Run > cmd.
Type in ipconfig´ It will say your default gateway, so type that in your browser and you will get a login screen. Skip the username part and fill inadmin´ at the password field.
Click the Applications & Gaming tab and fill in the things.
Start 43594
End 5555
Proctol = Both
IP Address = Your IP
And make sure you enable it!
